@startuml IWY_Interaction_Sequence
skinparam BoxPadding 10
actor "Glaucoma Patient" as User
participant "HUD Interface" as UI
participant "Camera/Hardware" as Camera
participant "Edge AI Model\n(YOLO/ML Kit)" as AI
participant "Audio Engine\n(TTS)" as TTS

User -> UI: Double Tap (Mode Toggle)
UI -> UI: Toggle Mode (Safety <-> OCR)
UI -> User: Visual Update: Change Overlay Transparency
UI -> TTS: Announce: "Mode Switched"
activate TTS
TTS --> User: Audio: "Text Scan Mode"
deactivate TTS

User -> UI: Single Tap (Scan Environment)
UI -> Camera: Request High-Res Frame
activate Camera
Camera --> UI: Native Image Buffer
deactivate Camera

UI -> AI: Send Image for Local Inference
activate AI
note right of AI: Processes 100% locally\n(No Cloud Latency)
AI --> UI: Return JSON (Boxes/Text/Confidence)
deactivate AI

UI -> UI: Aggregate Spatial Data\n(Calculate Left/Right, Near/Far)
UI -> UI: Render Neon-Yellow\nBounding Boxes on HUD
UI -> TTS: Dispatch Computed Summary String
activate TTS
TTS --> User: Audio: "Chair left, Person center"
deactivate TTS
@enduml
